{"tid":1827601,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍證實11名士兵在伊朗導彈襲擊行動中腦震盪","createTime":"2020-01-17T05:29:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T05:59:30.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"db1705759c84fc8b692a67f3e8eea8453393ae8e","tid":1827601,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T05:29:52.000Z","msg":"美軍證實，伊朗早前以導彈襲擊駐伊拉克美軍基地，導致11名美軍腦震盪，需要接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n伊朗今個月8日向美軍駐伊拉克的阿薩德基地發射導彈，報復美國擊殺革命衛隊「聖城旅」指揮官蘇萊馬尼，伊朗國營傳媒曾經聲稱擊斃80名美軍，並摧毀多架直升機及無人機，但美國總統特朗普否認有美國人員傷亡，軍事基地亦只是輕微受損。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503302-20200117.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503302-20200117.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcykzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=4cf2972a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503302-20200117.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=dd51891e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503302-20200117.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"32a57edd8115d5944840686644c9d2e5c8a0d43b","tid":1827601,"uid":219010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T05:35:01.000Z","msg":"同美帝一戰開戰原因幾似wo 唔通<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ec1e1dd7cd9a65d7355998a8b5e59a444fd02a3","tid":1827601,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T05:35:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9440b769afe07a18e7c82f3e4b5f8fe55ffb72d3","tid":1827601,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T05:53:38.000Z","msg":"Brain-storm?"},{"pid":"bae90b2ec3116aa21d040ae7e0895a777c33fa5d","tid":1827601,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9440b769afe07a18e7c82f3e4b5f8fe55ffb72d3","tid":1827601,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T05:53:38.000Z","msg":"Brain